{"data":{"page":{"id":"e1eb6785-9bbb-5ad0-9788-b030aea183c6","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://lapcm.herokuapp.com\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived website</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ea60635cf11720018893992a653b3299/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ea60635cf11720018893992a653b3299/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/ea60635cf11720018893992a653b3299/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>As part of my involvement with La PCM, I built a Wordpress website to help raise awareness of the organisation objectives. The website features a classic blog and some static pages with a carousel and forms to contact or subscribe.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2009"},"frontmatter":{"title":"La PCM","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/8d752a308144d022440e901e9cb77a0c/039c6/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lapcm/","source":"work"}}